Day 83 of posting daily until I reach 5k followers! 

*YOU HEARD ME SCREAMING MY LUNGS OUT* 😭🤧

Someone please pinch me, I don't believe it yet!

This is surreal, getting a gift from your dream brand, literally crying, shaking and overwhelmed @rarebeauty isn't just a bougie celebrity brand for me, it's a vision, support system and a family to me, where I feel safe and can be vulnerable, the kindness, humbleness, positivity that been imbibed in me is cos of them, they've helped me be a better version of myself, I can go forever and ever and take about them! If you ever gonna see the real essence, homely feeling of Rare Beauty, attend their #rarechat

Coming to this might gift, so here's how it goes, I received a letter from FedEx to claim a package on 5th, upon checking I found it was a package from Rare Beauty and the next thing shocked me to core, the package was sent in March 😳 
The level of anxiety got after hearing that Rare Beauty package in my name is lying at customs was another level!
Contacted courier company, they asked to mail them and and what they told shocked me to core, they asked 5k to reactivate the 7 month old package and I lost hope that I could even get and and gave up but as I said " Whats meant for you will reach you sooner or later" !!

Now peeps will be like how I got Rare Beauty package!
It's from @tyb.xyz community, i with folded hands request don't join Tyb community to get pr from them, it's a community not a brand work platform, by joining the community nobody is entitled a gift from them, there are 34k+ members you can think for yourselves

Satisfying sweet cravings without calories with @indewild 🍬 

@indewild Dewy Lip Treatment in Glazed Jalebi ✨
Intense Hydration for Soft, Plump Lips
Key Ingredients: Shea Butter, Peptides, Squalane, Hyaluronic Acid, mimicking Desi Ghee
Benefits: Repairs and hydrates dry lips
Texture: Rich, buttery balm
How to Use: Apply a generous layer before bed or throughout the day as needed 
Available in Tints - Wedding Rose, Caffeine Addict, Masala Chai

My thoughts:-
Initially I wasn't hit by the virality of this product until I myself tried it and omg it's too good!!
No, it doesn't smell or taste like jalebi but that shine it gives is unreal, not chunky but tiny glitters; fragrance and unflavoured 
And omg yes it's, very hydrating and makes my lips soft and supple, just yesterday only I applied it and could still feel that layer even after my lunch, it lasted that long! 

I'm very impressed with this and can't wait to get more of these, eyeing to get dirty chai next cos @globalbeautyfinds suggested 😉

 Don't forget to grab this in Summer Sale and get upto 35% off on site 🛍️
